    <div id="main_content"> 
     <h2>The Chicago Manual of Style Online</h2> 
     <p id="first">Completely searchable and easy to use, <i>The Chicago Manual of Style Online</i> provides recommendations on editorial style and publishing practices for the digital age. Now offering the full contents of the 16th and 15th editions, it is the must-have reference for everyone who works with words.</p> 
     <p class="link"> <a href="home.html" onclick="javascript:window.open('http://www.chicagomanualofstyle.org/sitetour/index.html','sitetour','width=860,height=640,top=100,left=200,menubar=yes,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes')"><img src="images/take_a_tour_OFF.gif" alt="TAKE A TOUR" class="rollover"></a> <img class="spacer" src="images/spacer_homepage.gif" alt="Spacer"> <a href="http://press-booksweb.uchicago.edu/MOSSSF/FreeTrial.aspx"><img src="images/free_trial_OFF.gif" alt="SIGN UP FOR A FREE TRIAL" border="0" class="rollover"></a> <img class="spacer" src="images/spacer_homepage.gif" alt="Spacer"> <a href="subscription_opts.html"><img src="images/sub_options_OFF.gif" alt="BUY AN ONLINE SUBSCRIPTION" class="rollover"></a> 
      <!--<a href="home.html"  onClick="javascript:window.open('http://www.chicagomanualofstyle.org/sitetour/index.html','sitetour','width=860,height=640,top=100,left=200,menubar=yes,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes')"><img src="images/take_a_tour_OFF.gif"  alt="TAKE A TOUR" class="rollover"></a>   --> <img class="spacer" src="images/spacer_homepage.gif" alt="Spacer"> 
